'''布罗德曼44区'''（英文：Brodmann area 44），简称'''BA44'''，是[[大脑皮质|大脑皮质]]的[[额叶|额叶]]的一个细胞结构分区，[[布罗德曼分区系统|布罗德曼分区系统]]中的第44区<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=Brodmann Area 44 - an overview|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/neuroscience/brodmann-area-44|access-date=2022-05-03|work=ScienceDirect|archive-date=2022-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220503044005/https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/neuroscience/brodmann-area-44}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Area 44 of Brodmann|url=http://braininfo.rprc.washington.edu/centraldirectory.aspx?ID=2402|access-date=2022-05-03|work=[[华盛顿大学|华盛顿大学]]|language=en|archive-date=2021-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210413073738/http://braininfo.rprc.washington.edu/centraldirectory.aspx?ID=2402}}</ref>。它位于[[額葉|额叶]]的外侧部，[[前运动区|前运动区]]之前，[[布罗德曼9区|布罗德曼9区]]之下，[[布罗德曼45区|布罗德曼45区]]之后<ref name=":0" />。

== 结构 ==
布罗德曼44区的上界为[[额下沟|额下沟]]，前界为[[外侧沟|外侧沟]]的上升枝。BA44在深度上延伸到[[岛叶|岛叶]]之界。该区域亦称为[[额下回|额下回]]的'''[[岛盖|岛盖部]]'''。布罗德曼44区是[[岛盖|额岛盖]]（Frontal operculum）的一部分。<ref name=":0" />

== 功能 ==
在[[人腦|人脑]]中，布罗德曼44区与45区一起组成[[布洛卡區|布洛卡区]]，与[[语言|语言]]处理有关；有数据表明BA44与[[语音|语音]]的关系较其与[[语法|语法]]的关系更为密切<ref name=":1" /><ref>{{Cite journal|title=The role of the left Brodmann's areas 44 and 45 in reading words and pseudowords|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/16310346/|last=Heim|first=Stefan|last2=Alter|first2=Kai|date=2005-12|journal=Brain Research. Cognitive Brain Research|issue=3|doi=10.1016/j.cogbrainres.2005.09.022|volume=25|pages=982–993|issn=0926-6410|pmid=16310346|last3=Ischebeck|first3=Anja K.|last4=Amunts|first4=Katrin|last5=Eickhoff|first5=Simon B.|last6=Mohlberg|first6=Hartmut|last7=Zilles|first7=Karl|last8=von Cramon|first8=D. Yves|last9=Friederici|first9=Angela D.|access-date=2022-05-03|archive-date=2021-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211104045158/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/16310346/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Higher Cortical Functions: Language (Section 4, Chapter 8) Neuroscience Online: An Electronic Textbook for the Neurosciences {{!}} Department of Neurobiology and Anatomy - The University of Texas Medical School at Houston|url=https://nba.uth.tmc.edu/neuroscience/m/s4/chapter08.html|access-date=2022-05-03|work=nba.uth.tmc.edu|archive-date=2021-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210413162531/https://nba.uth.tmc.edu/neuroscience/m/s4/chapter08.html}}</ref>。有研究显示，该区域还与手部运动有关<ref>{{cite journal|title=Motor and cognitive functions of the ventral premotor cortex|journal=Current Opinion in Neurobiology|issue=2|doi=10.1016/S0959-4388(02)00308-2|year=2002|volume=12|pages=149–154|pmid=12015230|author3=Gallese, V.|author1=Rizzolatti, G.|author2=Fogassi, L.|s2cid=17840974}}</ref>。

